Tages was a Swedish pop group formed in the early sixties near Gothenburg.
The band released a number of singles and LPs in their native Sweden to
considerable success, making the Swedish Top Ten more than a dozen times. <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tages_(band)" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tages_(band)</a>
